document_data.name: Du-yang
document_data.mainbody:
'''Du-yang''' was a prince of the kingdom of [[Silla]] in the land of [[Choson]] (later known as [[Koryo]]) before the midâ€“14th century [[DR]].

Under the influence of a love potion from the [[Quang Muku Forest]], Prince Du-yang of Silla fell in love with a plotting woman and was slain by her jealous husband.
